title: Judge Dredd versus the East-Megs Volume 1
description:
This will be the first of the complete collection of Judge Dredd story arcs involving the East Megs. In this volume:

1: Luna City One (Tour of Duty) progs 0042-0058 (1978)

2: Battle of the Black Atlantic - progs 0128-0129 (1980)

3: Pirates of the Black Atlantic - progs 0197-0200 (1981)

4: Block Mania - progs 0236-0244 (1981)

5: Apocalypse War - progs 0236-0244 (1982)
